— days or weeks, not quarters. Then STOP.

DO NOT WRITE A CLOSING PARAGRAPH.
DO NOT WRITE A BRIDGE TO THE NEXT CHAPTER.
DO NOT WRITE "AND THAT'S HOW YOU…"
DO NOT WRITE A SUMMARY.

When the test is described, the chapter is finished. Target: ~420
words. Gate `terminates_on_build_test` enforces this.
-->

{{test}}

